Shop RHW is a Toronto-based studio with a focus on solid wood custom furniture hand crafted by Rundell Haynes-Wells. 
In addition to being a craftsman, he also offers custom design consultation and renderings.

Rundell combines years of experience problem solving, exploring, and innovating, and has been a maker of things all of his life. 
He’s a natural born collaborator and is generous with the information he shares with his clients in the hope that more knowledge and understanding of custom furniture will inspire sustained interest and appreciation.

profile:
Welcome to IKEA Furniture Assembly Service - www.ASSEMBLYman.ca!

BOUGHT IKEA? Didn’t expect it to come in a whole bunch of pieces?

Don’t spend your weekend scratching your head over the furniture assembly. Call expert technicians and be SURE it’s done right the first time.

We are your GTA and surrounding areas IKEA Furniture Assembly and Installation specialists!

We assemble and install your IKEA kitchens, bathroom, BESTA system, PAX system, MALM, HOPEN, GALANT, Expedit or anything else you may have! 

If you see it in the IKEA catalog, we can assemble it, install it, hang it,snap it together, or simply place it where you like!

We offer the most competitive rates for IKEA Custom Assembly and Installation in the Great Toronto and surrounding areas. 

Assembly rates starting as low as $175.

Assembly - the proper way!
IKEA MAN will come to your house, as neat as a pin, as cool as a cucumber and get the job done before you've even put the tea on!
Ok, so maybe not that fast, but you get the idea.
*IKEA trained specialists with over 7 years of experience in IKEA Furniture Assembly
*Honest, reliable, professionally trained and equipped assemblers
*Peace of mind that someone you can trust is working in your home
*Specializing on IKEA Furniture Assembly and Installation
*Flexible and extended work hours to meet any service request needs
*We always get the job done, right, first time

profile:
Statum Designs Inc. is a Canadian owned corporation established in 1985. As a leading furniture manufacturer, Statum Designs Inc. has maintained its position by ensuring a continued focus on product quality that customers have come to know and appreciate.

By continuously creating an innovative product that is current with existing trends, Statum Designs Inc. has become a first choice for consumers.

Statum Designs Inc. offers a range of products that include sofas, loveseats and chairs as well as multiple configuration sectionals.  Products are available in an array of styles to accommodate any lifestyle.  Customers can choose from a more traditional product line or a more transitional look depending on their personal and interior design styles.  For smaller spaces, Statum Designs Inc. provides an added benefit by offering alternatives to standard dimensions.  Many styles are offered in dimensions to fit in smaller living spaces.

Wide product and style selection, superior quality and flexibility have all contributed to Statum Designs Inc. reputation for high customer satisfaction.

-- Awards and Achievements --
** Proud to be an active member of the Canadian Home Furnishing Alliance (CHFA) formerly known as the Ontario Furniture Manufacturer’s Association (OFMA).
** Recipient of numerous Trillium Awards acknowledging design excellence and innovation in the Canadian furniture market.
